To Build yosys, you will need these utilities.

Deps: clang, python3, git, tcl, libreadline, bison, flex, make, mercurial (hg), xdot, gv


$make
$make install

To generate netlist for triton code


$yosys -p "synth_tritoncore -blif output.blif" input.v

Links:
https://github.com/JackDavidson/OpenFPGACore-TritonCore/tree/master/TritoncoreI
